<HEADLINE> Tunisia Wins Arab Club Soccer Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, September 5 (Xinhua) -- Tunisia's CS Sfax secured
the Arab Club soccer championship, played in Jeddah, Saudi Arabia
at the weekend.
</P>
