relations have made steady progress, with fruitful cooperation
carried out in various fields and close coordination conducted in
world affairs, Luo said, adding China is willing to work together
with Trinidad and Tobago for an overall and healthy relations in
the new century.
</P>
<P>
Theodore said China's successful experience in achieving
economic development and social progress is well worth drawing on
by Trinidad and Tobago, and he himself is willing to exert more
efforts to push forward relations between the two countries and
the two peoples. 
