<P>
Mrs. Chennault, born in 1925 in Beijing, married Mr. Chennault
in 1947.
</P>
<P>
After immigrating to America, Mrs. Chennault has played an
active role in China's political circle.
</P>
<P>
The heroic activities of Mr. Chennault in the Anti-Japanese War
contributed to the Sino-American friendship in the 20th century,
Mrs. Chennault said.
