rose 5.02 percent to close at 25.94 yuan.
</P>
<P>
Among the losers, Shanghai Port Machinery Co., Ltd. dropped 7.
03 percent to 15 yuan.
</P>
<P>
Homeway predicts that the market is to find a new support line
on Wednesday. 
