which the two countries will cooperate in the industry of paper,
leather tanning and chemical products. "Sudan has 70 percent of the
Arab world's livestock, thus Egypt is interested in setting up
tanning projects to make the best use of that resource," said
Minister of Industry Moustafa el-Refay.
</P>
<P>
