<HEADLINE> Beijing Higher Education Seekers Realize Dreams </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 5 (Xinhua) -- More than seventy three
percent of people seeking higher education in Beijing were
enrolled by colleges and universities this year.
</P>
<P>
