implementation of the electronic trade, which is to enable the
development of the small and middle-size units and the access to
the under globalization current milieus," Sandulescu stressed.
</P>
<P>
The seminars held by professors and researchers from Romania,
the United States, Italy, the Netherlands, and Britain approached
a wide scaled topics such as the economic and IT aspects, global
electronic trade, insurance system by Internet or trade orders by
mobile phones, as well as social, juridical aspects of the
implementation of such solutions. (Romania-1st European
Conference-Electronic Trade)
</P>
