shares put an abrupt end to London market's six-session winning
streak on the session.
</P>
<P>
The FTSE index of leading shares ended 45.6 points or 0.7
percent down at 6752.5, above the 6737.6 low on the day but well
down from a midsession probe up to 6809.5.
</P>
<P>
