points, to 7395.07, hit by falls at index heavyweights Allianz and
Deutsche Telekom.
</P>
<P>
The Paris CAC-40 index closed nearly one percent lower as a
weak telecoms sector weighed on bourses across Europe. The index
closed at 6856.76 points, down 65.57 or 0.95 percent. 
