<HEADLINE> U.N. Chief Meets Iran's President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A statement from the U.N. spokesman's office said that in the
meeting, the secretary-general and the president of Iran raised
the issue of Afghanistan, and they discussed joint peace efforts
by the U.N. and the Organization of the Islamic Conference, which
Iran currently chairs.
</P>
